{"tid":904483,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"細佬18歲人都成個小朋友咁，仲要無大無細","createTime":"2018-11-16T11:25:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-16T12:40:43.000Z","uid":199104,"like":3,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f22fce32a037dcb9422497add2bfe4f69cc0fa7a","tid":904483,"uid":199104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T11:25:10.000Z","msg":"點解我細佬可以成個小朋友咁？<br />\n其實佢已經18歲，<br />\n今年都考文憑試啦，<br />\n但佢仲係日日同佢女朋友拍拖，<br />\n日日出街，<br />\n從來無見過佢溫書，<br />\n又明知無可能考天才，<br />\n咁佢係想點呢？<br />\n<br />\n仲要無返兼識，<br />\n淨係成日伸手問呀媽拎錢。<br />\n到我開口話佢呢，<br />\n佢無大無細到話我做sales一樣無前途，<br />\n無資格話佢，<br />\n點解可以咁離譜？<br />\n<br />\n我怕佢玻璃心，<br />\n但我又好想話醒佢，<br />\n可以點做？"},{"pid":"c9bb2a3765e6984bbbe44fa615876f6a3d82e97f","tid":904483,"uid":109655,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T11:26:00.000Z","msg":"樓主毒撚冇女唔抵得人拍拖？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76fa4bddd5c556ba1f3076270553a716a5d62f47","tid":904483,"uid":199211,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T11:26:35.000Z","msg":"中學雞做乜pt 專心讀書啦"},{"pid":"4a39868123635a5de28eb829bd8c95d8e7d05133","tid":904483,"uid":78243,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T11:27:24.000Z","msg":"0/10"},{"pid":"f01a3be8c268df26a95809d173342a46c4d4ee2e","tid":904483,"uid":54812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T11:47:57.000Z","msg":"我都驚自己細佬變到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"457d1c7149adfb1781c8a12db6785aa5f7fe343b","tid":904483,"uid":165871,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T11:49:53.000Z","msg":"咁你的確無資格話佢既"},{"pid":"fdc585b86a1d8023b78e120e3e7ebfbeacaf9308","tid":904483,"uid":200603,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T11:50:23.000Z","msg":"屌你中學唔拍拖讀中學做咩"},{"pid":"c35e1333ac50ceda4a231b2afb95105ffed7d5f1","tid":904483,"uid":199104,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"45